Cooley:
Two foot prints hits the ground next to Camoflage, A reptilian style voice can be heard, "it's okay little one, you are safe now, Please calm down. What happened." He looked to the other Bot lying on the ground, "Oh god that is a problem," He smiles an unseen smile and yells, " SOMEBODY HELP OH MY GOD WE GOT A BLEEDER AND IT IS BAD," as he leans down for the bleeding bot. Takes off part of his chest plate and pulls out some emergency cable he has and begins to reroute the leaking fluid on KitKat so she would loose less fluid.

shadowess_azogoth <shadowess_azogoth@...> wrote:
Camoflage::

She sat crying in bot mode. "Please, why *sob* won't someone help 
us?"  She put a hand on KitKat's shoulder, "I'm so *sob* sorry. But 
they can't hear me I guess."

KitKat::
She moaned as her mech fluid levels dropped again. She lifted her 
head up and whispered, "It's alright, we must all greet the matrix at 
sometime. Thank ou for all that you have...."  She passed out.

Camoflage::

She started crying harder and whailing. She shook KitKat's body, "No, 
please don't go. I don't want to be alone out here again. No please."

KitKat::
She was alive, but in dire need of medical attention.
